description:
Available in 24 cities including New York, London, Moscow, St Petersburg, and all across Israel.

Get a luxurious black car instantly. $10 rides in Manhattan. Anywhere, Anytime.

“Editors' Choice” on App Store
Winner of Time Out magazine – Best App of the Year
Forbes: “GetTaxi - One of 15 explosively growing companies in 2013”

- No surge pricing
- No cancellation fees
- On demand or pre-book your ride
- Airport rides at fantastic flat rates
- 24/7 live customer support
- Invite friends and earn $20 every time they use your code
